{"questionId":"32399613","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Althea calculates the expected frequencies and records them in this table.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;\" src=\"__IMG__/228dd6ec55895ac467a5aaa44f318530f7da4d1d.png\" width=\"573\" height=\"82\"></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>state whether&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>k</mi></math> is positive, negative, or could be either</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>must be positive,&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>since&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>L</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>&nbsp; (and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>L</mi><mo>∞</mo></msub><mo>-</mo><mi>L</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>R1<br><br></strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Do not award <em><strong>A1R0</strong></em>.<br>Accept equivalent reasoning in words, e.g. the growth is positive.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"32399613","referenceCode":"24N.3.AHL.TZ0.2fi","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"state whether k is positive, negative, or could be either","paper":"3","level":"HL","questionNumber":"i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5—Calculus","Topic 5—Calculus","AHL 5.14—Setting up a DE, solve by separating variables"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":3}
